# Lightbar demo menu. STYLE LIGHTBAR runs a moving highlight over the
# |{R,C,K,Label} option markers the sysop placed in the SCREEN art -- the
# option positions live in the .pp, not the code. Hotkeys still work, and
# options whose ACS the caller fails are dropped from the bar automatically.
STYLE LIGHTBAR
SCREEN art/lbdemo.pp
KEY f - GOTO FILEMENU
KEY m - GOTO MSGMENU
KEY w - WHOSON
KEY g - GOTO MAIN
